Uh, Spears and co. were still at the Ark, wern't they?

::Firearm::

Firearm growls as Spears runs off, hearing her yell.

"Let's go!" he says to Lunarpine, taking off and flying at Spears, his 
jetpack pushing him forward as he slowly gainst on her. He sets his arm 
cannon on charge launcher, ready to blast the ground near her if needed.
